      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total dream. This car is in stunning shape\u2014I've babied it since day one and it truly looks and feels like it just left the showroom! It\u2019s spotless inside and out, runs like a charm, and I\u2019ve kept up with every bit of maintenance. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I do. Shoot me a message if you want to come see this beauty in person!",
