    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable specimen of the S54-powered BMW M3. This unit features a meticulously maintained 3.2L straight-six with factory-spec compression across all cylinders and a fully serviced double VANOS system. The Getrag manual transmission operates with tactile precision, paired with a fresh clutch and a robust limited-slip differential. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to handle the high-torque output of the S54. All suspension components, including the bushings and dampers, retain their original damping rates and structural integrity. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, preserved in a condition that mirrors its factory rollout.",
      "price": 46500.0,
